@startuml
title 数据转换处理 - 通过处理器链转换传感器数据

participant "SensorDataRepository" as Repo
participant "ProcessorRegistry" as Registry
participant "ProcessorChain" as Chain
participant "HeartRateSmoother" as Smoother
participant "HeartRateAnalyzer" as Analyzer
participant "Room" as DB

Repo -> Registry: getChain(RawHeartRate::class)
Registry --> Repo: ProcessorChain
Repo -> Chain: execute(rawHeartRate)
Chain -> Smoother: process(RawHeartRate)
Smoother --> Chain: SmoothedHeartRate
Chain -> Analyzer: process(SmoothedHeartRate)
Analyzer --> Chain: HeartRateAlert
Chain --> Repo: 最终 ConsumableData
Repo -> DB: 存储结果
@enduml
